SUMMARY:Mat-Su Outdoorsman Show
DESCRIPTION:FRIDAY – NOON-6:00 \nSATURDAY – 10:00-6:00 \nSUNDAY – 10:00-5:00 \nADMISSION \nAdults-$10 \nMilitary w/ID-$5 \nUnder 12-FREE \nWe are excited to announce that the Mat-Su Outdoorsman Show is partnering with the Alaska Department of Fish and Game and the William Jack Hernandez Fish Hatchery to include a kid’s trout fishing pond at the Mat-Su Outdoorsman Show! \nChildren under 15 can fish for free and enjoy the thrill of catching and keeping (or releasing) one of 2\,000 rainbow trout during their visit to the show. The pond will be located outside\, near the popular food trucks\, boats\, and camper displays.
URL:https://www.connectmatsu.org/event/mat-su-outdoorsman-show-5/
END:VEVENT
