SUMMARY:Mat-Su College 2026 Spring Open House
DESCRIPTION:Ready to take the next step in your education? Whether you’re a high school student or looking to level up your career\, come and experience the atmosphere and community in action at Mat-Su College! Join us for our annual Spring Open House to explore our campus\, meet some faculty\, and get a head start on your future.
