SUMMARY:2026 Kickoff Kitchen
DESCRIPTION:Tickets for our 2026 Kickoff Kitchen fundraiser and annual Community Awards are ON SALE NOW!\nJoin us for this celebration of local volunteers\, businesses and community champions\, and our past year’s accomplishments. We are excited for another great event\, and to announce our Volunteer of the Year\, Dorothy A. Jones Lifetime Achievement Award\, Business Partner of the Year and Community Champion award winners.\nBring your best bidding face for our Live Auction\, try NOT to be outbid on the incredible desserts in our Dessert Auction\, and test your knowledge with Kathy’s trivia contest!  \n$70 individual\n$400 for a table of 6 \nSpecial thanks to Mat-Su Health Foundations \nQuestions? Please call (907)745-5822 or email give@unitedwaymatsu.org
URL:https://www.connectmatsu.org/event/2026-kickoff-kitchen/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=application/pdf:https://www.connectmatsu.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Kitchen-Kickoff.pdf
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR